pluginhost~ - a plugin host for Pure Data
==========================================

This directory (pluginhost) contains sourcecode and possibly binaries for a
plugin host for Pure Data. It currently supports the following plugin types:

  *  LADSPA:     http://www.ladspa.org/
  *  DSSI:       http://dssi.sourceforge.net/

The functionality of the external is demonstrated in in the help patch
(pluginhost/pluginhost~-help.pd).

WWW: https://github.com/BirminghamConservatoire/ix7/tree/master/pluginhost~
